{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act20side", "eventName": "理想城：長夏狂歡季", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IC-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "生活之道", "storyInfo": "杜林人們開始著手打扮城市的遺容，阿芙朵嘉也在思考著如何向市民們傳達自己的想法，而斯第奇卻在壓力之下選擇了逃避。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_caveentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，耶奇大師，我有點好奇，斯第奇的師父，是個什麼樣的人？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就知道你小子跟我來有別的目的。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很關心斯第奇那小子啊。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，被您看出來了嗎。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這個人就是這樣，希望大家都能和和氣氣地搞好關係。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你一定會喜歡他的師父的。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#10$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "芬奇·畫布，是際崖城最受歡迎的建築設計師。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的設計風格雖然和杜林中最流行的風格迥異，但在他的解釋下，卻總是能抓住大夥的心。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用他的話說，叫什麼來著，對了，“對抗我們無休止的欲望”。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然他的理論比較獨特，但際崖城的人都很喜歡他。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這樣的人為什麼會離開際崖城？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道欸。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#6$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#7$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他忽然就離開了，沒有告訴任何人。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......還真是奇怪。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#12$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#12$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他留下的這個徒弟呢，雖然才華大家都是認可的，但是人嘛，你也看到了。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，大概這也和他老師的突然離開有關吧。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰說不是呢。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#2$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_medicalbeep", "channel": "a", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？是不是出結果了？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，讓我看看......", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#9$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#11$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，和我預測的差不多。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還有將近一個月的時間。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個月？那應該足夠擴建升降梯了吧。", "name": "嘉維爾"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來了，嘉維爾。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，不過看來已經不用我幫忙了？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，勘測到這一步就差不多了。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說服阿芙朵嘉了？", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，她說她會幫忙說服際崖城的居民們。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，那剩下的應該就是正式通知全城的居民這個狀況了。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅要決定是不是前往地面，穹頂的事情也得解決掉。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？關穹頂什麼事？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，我都快要忘了你們不是杜林了。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杜林人的城市雖然說不經常遭難，但一個杜林，在一生中往往難免要面對一次自己居住城市的毀滅。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們對於離開家鄉這件事並不會有什麼感想。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相反，我們在離開前，總是要將自己的城市維持在最好的狀態，讓它能夠以最好的狀態迎接毀滅。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來很酷嘛！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？對我們來說，這是理所當然的事。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而穹頂上的那個洞，之前放著不管有它的理由，現在就要想想辦法了。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到穹頂，斯第奇呢？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？他不是跟你們在一起嗎？", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？他說來找你們了啊。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘉維爾，你要找斯第奇嗎？", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道他去哪了？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。我們進來的時候遇到他了，他沒跟我們說話，只是往洞窟外面去了。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#6$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g5_library_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你信誓旦旦地跟我們說你有地圖，結果現在又告訴我們，地圖有可能在這一面書架上某本書裡？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，這也是沒有辦法的事。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟我對於返回地上沒有任何興趣，能夠記得曾經在書裡看到過前人記錄下來的路線圖這件事本身，你們就該知足了。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間還有一些，如果那個洞穴結構真有你們說的那麼複雜，我也不介意在這裡多花一些時間。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你還記得那本書到底叫什麼嗎？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忘了。我隱隱約約記得應該是一本遊記，上面講述了身為杜林的作者在地表的種種經歷。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問了也沒用吧，我們又不懂杜林語。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我不懂，但不要忘了，我有這些朋友。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_robotwalk"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_576_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祖瑪瑪，祖瑪瑪，需要幫忙？", "name": "奇怪的機械0429"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要找一本阿芙朵嘉說的，記錄了前往地表的洞穴結構路線圖的遊記。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_576_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖書館，不常整理書籍，尋找難度，較高。", "name": "奇怪的機械"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到的話，我會幫你們做一次大維護。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_576_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祖瑪瑪，朋友，幫助祖瑪瑪。", "name": "奇怪的機械0429"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_576_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫助祖瑪瑪，幫助祖瑪瑪。", "name": "奇怪的機械"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，那你們加油，我在外面等你們，有麻煩記得喊我。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及......大祭司。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_074", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在，我在。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來幫忙。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......？！", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的朋友。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_074"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不應該首先問我懂不懂杜林語嗎，祖瑪瑪。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有可能不懂嗎？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_074"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噢，你還在因為我沒有告訴你地下的事生氣嗎。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事情是這樣的，祖瑪瑪，如果我要把我知道的東西全都告訴你，那可能直到你能造出移動城市的那一天都說不完。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我個人認為對於知識的瞭解是需要點到為止的，雖然我不是人。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫不幫？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_074"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果找到了你就原諒我的話。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成交。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g1_durinstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，依娜姆，你怎麼站在圖書館的門口？", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這裡等人，你呢？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖書館的管理人喊我過來，商討一下有關圖書館改建的事。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他早就想做了，結果一直拖著，這次倒是一個好機會。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我之前就有點好奇了。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "距離之前的廣播已經過去了大半天，城裡的杜林沒有慌張也就算了。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼一個兩個都在盤算著改建自己的房子？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？噢，你是地上人，大概確實沒法理解。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是造了可以移動的城市來躲避災難的，對吧？", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們不一樣，我們的城市是無法移動的。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在地下建造的城市，要移動起來確實更加困難。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我聽說也不是沒有大師想過要建造那種城市。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，如果給穹頂加上碎岩和鑿壁之類的功能，再給城市加上底盤，其實好像也不是不能實現嘛。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......我不太懂建築，但是這聽起來比我們的移動城市還要瘋狂。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實際上到現在我也沒聽說真的有人造出了這樣的城市就是啦。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，我們的城市是無法移動的。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我們每座城市都會有檢測源石礦脈的設施，在檢測到源石礦脈靠近時，就會預警。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個設施是不是能替代天災信使的工作啊......", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說過天災信使的存在，其實是不太一樣的，因為這個設施只能檢測源石礦脈的蔓延。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這倒也是。從聽說的情況來看，源石礦脈在被發現後距離活化還有一段時間，如果不是這次這樣的特殊情況，是完全足夠你們撤離的。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而天災一旦發現端倪，就已經很難有這樣的時間了。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你們已經習慣了放棄自己的城市？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實恰恰相反。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杜林熱愛與這片土地有關的一切，我們熱愛機械，熱愛建築，熱愛我們建造的每一座城市。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#2$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果災難無法避免，我們的城市註定被毀滅。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#2$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們必然要面對這個現實，那我們就必須思考一個問題。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一座城市的居民會因為災難而離開，但災難只是一時的，會有其他杜林，甚至他們的子孫後代重新來到這片土地。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會看到城市的遺骸，他們會為此地的災難而哀歎，但我們作為曾經生活在這座城市裡的人，想要他們體會到的，當真只有這些嗎？", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於無法逃避的命運，我們只能選擇服從嗎？", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不接受這種做法，我們選擇——", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在災難降臨之前，我們將決定，我們的城市會以何種面貌迎接毀滅。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要讓後來者讚美我們技術的結晶，我們要讓他們驚歎於我們留下的痕跡，我們要讓他們為我們的成就暢飲一杯美酒。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我們看到其他隕落的城市時，也會這麼去做一樣。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們當然會因為背井離鄉而感到悲傷，但我們已經習慣了這種悲傷。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，對我們來說，在這個時刻，讓我們的城市保持最好的狀態，是一件更有意義的事情，不是嗎？", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是所謂的，打扮城市的遺容。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還真是......浪漫的想法。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然啦，更直接的原因是，只要我們帶好關鍵的工業裝備，在機器人們的幫助下，幾個月我們就能快速重建一座新的城市。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則，我們肯定是沒有資本去這麼想的啦。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，這倒也是。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，那是......斯第奇？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g5_library_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$book_close"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本......不對。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$book_close"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本，也不對。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "Sound_Beta_2/Player/p_atk/p_atk_book_n"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本，咦，這本怎麼會在這？之後帶回去吧。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本書，是卡西米爾的騎士小說......你的？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，忘了你至少認得這個......", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是吧，我從地上帶下來的。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說起來......", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一個烏薩斯人，到底是怎麼從烏薩斯一路流落到杜林城邦的？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的家人都死在了一場毫無榮耀可言的貴族鬥爭裡，而我被迫逃離我的家鄉。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在逃亡過程中，我被殺手逼迫，逃進了一座洞穴。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那座洞穴的結構就和這座升降梯上方的洞穴一樣複雜，而我偶然發現了通往地底的升降梯。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這樣，我幸運地生存了下來，就這麼簡單。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，那你確實挺走運的。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你沒有別的感想嗎？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你希望我有什麼感想嗎？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉，你果然還是那個嘉維爾的朋友。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在羅德島上聽說過不少類似的故事。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你活下來了這件事本身，就足夠幸運了。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#7$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "際崖城是個好地方，在這樣的地方生活，挺好的。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是啊。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來以為，我會對自己的境遇更加憤怒的。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，難道我的家庭竟是如此無辜，我的父母平日樂善好施，卻被邪惡的人仇恨嗎？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然不是。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的父親，直到最後的時刻，比起關心自己的家人，依然在詛咒著他的對手。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的母親，當我從後門逃出家裡的時候，我甚至不知道她人在何方。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我，我不過是諸多烏薩斯貴族陰謀中的一個微不足道的犧牲品罷了。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得對，我很幸運，所以，我必須珍惜我來之不易的幸運。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你其實很想和嘉維爾大吵一架，對吧？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......何以見得？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為你雖然被她說服了，但是仔細想想，你想說的事情其實沒有真正說出來。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想要再去找她理論時，卻又失去了時機，於是就只能自己憋著。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見過很多被嘉維爾那種性格氣到的人，我偶爾也會，而你屬於最明顯的那一種。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好吧，我承認。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從沒見過嘉維爾那樣的人，無論是我作為烏薩斯人的一面，還是我作為杜林人的一面，都拿她有些......沒有辦法。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你真的有什麼不吐不快的想法，可以告訴我，你幫了我的忙，我會考慮幫你傳達給她。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......免了，我還沒有淪落到這種地步。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我有一個提議。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並沒有真正回到地上生活的打算。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等到危機過去後，我也會建議杜林返回地下。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，聯繫一旦建立，就無法輕易被切斷，從此斷絕往來幾乎是不可能的，這一點我也理解。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我承認，你們，阿卡胡拉的提亞卡烏或許是可以交流的對象。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#10$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，等到杜林在地下重建自己的城市後，我想邀請你們從一無所有的雨林中搬遷到地下來。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#10$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那時，即使是嘉維爾這樣的人，也一定能夠理解，杜林的社會是多麼美好。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#10$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#10$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......那還是免了吧。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是先找到地圖再說吧。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}